      "text": "Packet Replay\n• Preserves inter-packet timing  (time.sleep on gap_us)\n• Tags every 25th sender as Control  (DSCP 46),  rest Bulk  (DSCP 0)\n• Wire format:  size_bytes, traffic_class, priority_tag\\n",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Packet Replay\n• Preserves inter-packet timing  (time.sleep on gap_us)\n• Tags every 25th sender as Control  (DSCP 46),  rest Bulk  (DSCP 0)\n• Wire format:  size_bytes, traffic_class, priority_tag\\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aP",
      "autoResize": true
    },
