      "text": "Queue w/ CPU priority sort\n───────────\nstd::sort  (introsort)\nSort interval: 9000 µs\nBuffer: 50 MB\nLink: 45 Gbps\nPriority: DSCP 46 = ctrl\nBlind window =\nmeasured sort time\n(~50 µs avg)",
