      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Queue w/ GPU priority sort\n───────────\nThrust radix sort  (CUDA)\nSort interval: 9000 µs\nBuffer: 50 MB\nLink: 45 Gbps\nPriority: DSCP 46 = ctrl\nBlind window =\nGPU kernel time\n(~5 µs avg)\nPinned memory\n(cudaHostAlloc)\nPipeline parallelism\n(3 async CUDA streams)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Queue w/ GPU priority sort\n───────────\nThrust radix sort  (CUDA)\nSort interval: 9000 µs\nBuffer: 50 MB\nLink: 45 Gbps\nPriority: DSCP 46 = ctrl\nBlind window =\nGPU kernel time\n(~5 µs avg)\nPinned memory\n(cudaHostAlloc)\nPipeline parallelism\n(3 async CUDA streams)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "ae",
